  "text": "To delineate between two members of MAC: i.e., M. avium subspecies paratuberculosis and M. avium subsp. avium which could not be differentiated by the genus specific 16S rDNAsequencing assay, the MYCGEN-MYCAV PCR as described by [CITATION_1] as well as amplification of the IS900 of the M. avium subsp. paratuberculosis [CITATION_2] was conducted in two separate PCR reactions using primers described below:",
